sentences.english: The feasibility study of a new airport in Wuhan was also complete by them.
sentences.chinese: 武汉新机场的可行性研究也是他们作的。

sentences.english: The paper studied the covered material thickness of the frozen sugarbeet storage.
sentences.chinese: 本文对甜菜冻藏长期保管的苫盖厚度做一可行性研究。

sentences.english: Feasibility Research on Beef Processing in Datu.
sentences.chinese: 丹徒县肉牛加工项目的可行性研究。

sentences.english: Economic evaluation is one of the important contents.
sentences.chinese: 经济评价是可行性研究的重要内容之一。

sentences.english: The second part is the case of Chlorine-Alkali project of ShanDong DongYue Group .
sentences.chinese: 第二部分为山东东岳集团氯碱项目可行性研究案例。

sentences.english: Most decisions are made based on research and feasibility studies and are implemented thoroughly without resistance.
sentences.chinese: 多数决定是在研究和可行性研究和实施没有抵抗到底。

sentences.english: But this is only at an early stage of feasibility study.
sentences.chinese: 但是这仅仅处于可行性研究的初期阶段。

sentences.english: The feasibility study and draft design of China's aircraft carrier started in 1992.
sentences.chinese: 可行性研究和设计图稿中国航空母舰始于1992年。

sentences.english: The contents of project funds application are basically the same as the feasibility study.
sentences.chinese: 资金申请报告的研究内容与可行性研究基本相同。

sentences.english: A feasibility study is being carried out before we invest in the new leisure centre.
sentences.chinese: 在投资新休闲中心前，我们正作项目可行性研究。

sentences.english: In this paper, weld seam tracking method based on microbeam plasma arc is developed.
sentences.chinese: 进行了基于微束等离子弧的焊缝跟踪传感可行性研究。

sentences.english: Complete the feasible research report, the job-site is available in current time.
sentences.chinese: 已完成可行性研究报告，有现成场地。

sentences.english: Feasibility Research on flower Production in Wuxi Mashon.
sentences.chinese: 无锡市马山花卉生产项目的可行性研究。

sentences.english: Forcasted Producing Scale is provided in the Feasibility Study Report.
sentences.chinese: 预计生产规模在可行性研究报告中规定。
